quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  72,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  72,1,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho, meri taraf wahi bhaije gayi hai ke junoo ke aik giroh ne ghhor se suna phir ( ja kar apni qoum ke logon se ) kaha :"" hum ne aik bara hi ajeeb quran suna hai"
  72,2,"jo raah raast ki taraf rahnumai karta hai iss liye hum uss par imaan le aeye hain aur ab hum hargiz apne rab ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karen ge """
  72,3,"aur yeh ke"" hamaray rab ki shaan bohat aala o Arfah hai, uss ne kisi ko biwi ya beta nahi banaya hai """
  72,4,"aur yeh ke"" hamaray nadaan log Allah ke baray mein bohat khilaaf haq baatein kehte rahay hain """
  72,5,"aur yeh ke"" hum ne samgha tha ke ensaan aur jin kabhi khuda ke baray mein jhoot nahi bol satke """
  72,6,"aur yeh ke"" insanon mein se kuch log junoo mein se kuch logon ki panah manga karte thay, iss terhan onhon ne junoo ka ghuroor aur ziyada barha diya """
  72,7,"aur yeh ke"" insanon ne bhi wohi gumaan kya jaissa tumhara gumaan tha ke Allah kisi ko rasool bana kar nah beje ga """
  72,8,"aur yeh ke"" hum ne aasman ko tatola to dekha ke woh pehray daaron se pita para hai aur shahbon(Aag ke angaroon) ki barish ho rahi hai """
  72,9,"aur yeh ke"" pehlay hum sun gun lainay ke liye aasman mein bethnay ki jagah pa letay thay, magar ab jo chori chupay suneney ki koshish karta hai woh apne liye ghaat mein aik Shahab Saqib laga howa paata hai """
  72,10,"aur yeh ke"" hamari samajh mein nah aata tha ke aaya zameen walon ke sath koi bura maamla karne ka iradah kya gaya hai ya unn ka rab unhen raah raast dikhnana chahta hai """
  72,11,"aur yeh ke"" hum mein se kuch log Saleh hain aur kuch is se frotar hain, hum mukhtalif tareeqon mein battay hue hain """
  72,12,"aur yeh ke"" hum samajte thay ke nah zameen mein hum Allah ko aajiz kar satke hain aur nah bhaag kar ussay hara satke hain """
  72,13,"aur yeh ke"" hum ne jab hadaayat ki taleem suni to hum is par imaan le aeye ab jo koi bhi apne rab par imaan le aeye ga usay kisi haq talfi ya zulm ka khauf nah hoga """
  72,14,"aur yeh ke"" hum mein se kuch muslim ( Allah ke itaat guzaar ) hain aur kuch haq se munharif to jinhon ne islam ( itaat ka rasta ) ikhtiyar kar liya unhon ne nijaat ki raah dhoond li"
  72,15,"aur jo haq se munharif hain woh jahannum ka eendhan ban'nay walay hain """
  72,16,"aur ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho, mujh par yeh wahi bhi ki gayi hai ke ) log agar raah raast par saabit qadmi se chaltay to hum unhen khoob sairaab karte"
  72,17,taakay is Nemat se un ki azmaish karen aur jo apne rab ke zikar se mun moray ga is ka rab usay sakht azaab mein mubtala kar day ga
  72,18,"aur yeh ke masjiden Allah ke liye hain, lehaza unn mein Allah ke sath kisi aur ko nah poukaro"
  72,19,aur yeh ke jab Allah ka bandah uss ko pukarnay ke liye khara howa to log uss par toot parney ke liye tayyar ho gay
  72,20,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho ke"" mein to apne rab ko pukaarta hon aur is ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karta """
  72,21,"kaho,"" mein tum logon ke liye nah kisi nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar rakhta hon nah kisi bhalai ka """
  72,22,"kaho,"" mujhe Allah ki girift se koi nahi bacha sakta aur nah mein uss ke daman ke siwa koi jaye panah pa sakta hon"
  72,23,"mera kaam is ke siwa kuch nahi hai ke Allah ki baat aur is ke paighamaat pouncha dun ab jo bhi Allah aur is ke rasool ki baat nah manay ga is ke liye jahannum ki aag hai aur aisay log is mein hamesha rahen ge """
  72,24,( yeh log apni iss rawish se baz nah ayen ge ) yahan taq ke jab uss cheez ko dekh len ge jis ka inn se wada kya ja raha hai to inhen maloom ho jaye ga ke kis ke madadgaar kamzor hain aur kis ka jatha tadaad mein kam hai
  72,25,"kaho,"" mein nahi jaanta ke jis cheez ka wada tum se kya ja raha hai woh qareeb hai ya mera rab is ke liye koi lambi muddat muqarrar farmata hai"
  72,26,"woh a'lam ul ghiab hai, apne ghaib par kisi ko mutala nahi karta"
  72,27,"siwaye uss rasool ke jisay uss ne ( ghaib ka koi ilm dainay ke liye ) pasand kar liya ho, to uss ke agay aur peechay woh Muhafiz laga deta hai"
  72,28,"taakay woh jaan le ke unhon ne apne rab ke paighamaat pouncha diye, aur woh unn ke poooray mahol ka ihata kiye hue hai aur aik aik cheez ko is ne gun rakha hai """
